Jody, Sara Young Schott, Stan, and the whole family have been great to deal with and are making huge waves in the bull industry. We will continue to train futurity bulls and make a bigger push with our rider bulls! 
This is 117K a maiden prospect that may be the rankest calf I’ve raised and seen in awhile!Justin Cox has him firing on all cylinders. 
Sire:107X (88 Best Shot x K327)
Dam: 7v6 (67B Bumblebee x Oscars Velvet)

💥 We will be accepting outside calves to train starting after the @abbibulls finals. We currently have over 200 in training now and we would love to get your calves on the list. 
We have multiple different options to explore on how we charge so please give me a call or text with any questions. 
Also if you have PBR caliber rider bulls that you want hauled we have room on the truck for a handful more. 💥
